台灣女生很容易」上寫到，台女很容易相處、很容易玩開、很容易把，是世界上最美麗的女性之一。尼克拍攝的影片是透過他頭上的GoPro來記錄，觀眾可以看到尼克是如何跟亞洲女性搭訕，且不只有台女，日本、泰國、中國、韓國的女性都是他的目標。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\nTaking Easy Taiwan Girl Home From Club<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FpuKNw6a-eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFpuKNw6a-eI&d=aWLXTKQj1tRetMXIM7PMN49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4cb8e668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FpuKNw6a-eI</a><br />\n<br />\nI pull a cute 18 year old Taiwanese girl home within ten minutes of flirting and kissing in the night club in Taipei. <br />\n<br />\nTaiwan Landing Site Sales Video<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9H0GvWo4QSk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9H0GvWo4QSk&d=aWLXTKQj1tRetMXIM7PMN49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6e3e870e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9H0GvWo4QSk</a><br />\n28秒當中有懷疑床照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一睇就知 結局係點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洋腸會留係香港兩星期<br />\n一定大把本土A片大量流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家拭目以待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9daffd3d9a5495ca5fa6d13b5d53ca5960fc774c","tid":741442,"uid":57636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"如果大家撞到佢哋，不如喺呢到報告下佢哋行蹤<br />\n好